      • getPluginIconResource

        public static java.lang.String getPluginIconResource()
        Attempts to load the custom 4diac plugin icon.
        Returns:
        A String representing the relative path to the icon. If loading the custom 4diac plugin icon fails, a String representing the relative path to the default plugin controller icon is returned.
